text: Winkelhaid is a municipality in Nürnberger Land in Bavaria in Germany. It is 18 km southeast of Nuremberg in the Middle Franconia. Winkelhaid is bounded by (from the north and clockwise) Altdorf bei Nürnberg, Schwarzenbruck and Feucht. == Districts == * Penzenhofen * Richthausen * Ungelstetten * Winkelhaid ==References== Category:Nürnberger Land
